---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Intake Process Optimization for Law Firms | Hughey LLC"
  description="Redesign your intake process to convert more leads to clients. Faster qualification. Better data. Higher conversion rates."
  canonical="https://hugheyllc.com/services/intake-process-optimization"
>
  <div style="background: var(--ink); color: var(--white); min-height: 100vh;">
    <div style="min-height: 300px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.1) 0%, rgba(27, 51, 96, 0.15) 100%); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; padding: 80px 0;">
      <div class="w">
        <h1 style="font-size: clamp(42px, 6vw, 72px); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; max-width: 900px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
          Intake Process<br />Optimization
        </h1>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6); max-width: 700px; line-height: 1.6;">
          Your marketing drives leads but your intake process drops 30-40% of them. We redesign your intake workflow, implement technology, and train your team to convert more prospects into clients.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="padding: 80px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.15);">
      <div class="w">
        <div style="max-width: 900px;">
          <h2 style="font-size: 42px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 32px;">The Problem</h2>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85); margin-bottom: 20px;">
            Your marketing is driving 100 leads per month. But:
          </p>
          <ul style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 2; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85); margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
            <li>20 leads drop off because your intake form is too long</li>
            <li>15 leads are lost in the gap between form submission and phone call</li>
            <li>10 leads fall through because phone intake isn't consistent</li>
            <li>8 leads aren't followed up on because they're in multiple systems</li>
          </ul>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);">
            You're wasting 53% of your marketing budget. And even worse, you have no data about what type of prospect actually becomes a retained client—so you can't optimize your marketing to attract better prospects.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="padding: 80px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.15);">
      <div class="w">
        <div style="max-width: 900px;">
          <h2 style="font-size: 42px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 48px;">What We Do</h2>
          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(420px, 1fr)); gap: 40px;">
            <div>
              <h3 style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 12px;">Audit Current Process</h3>
              <p style="font-size: 15px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); line-height: 1.6;">
                We examine your forms, phone intake, coordinators, follow-up process, and CRM. We identify where leads are lost and why.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 12px;">Redesign Workflow</h3>
              <p style="font-size: 15px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); line-height: 1.6;">
                We create a new intake process optimized for conversion: shorter forms, faster phone contact, consistent qualification, better data capture.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 12px;">Implement Technology</h3>
              <p style="font-size: 15px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); line-height: 1.6;">
                We set up CRM, intake forms, phone systems, and integrations so data flows automatically and coordinators have all information they need.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 12px;">Train Your Team</h3>
              <p style="font-size: 15px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); line-height: 1.6;">
                We train coordinators on the new process and tools. We document the workflow. We set up metrics to track performance.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="padding: 80px 0;">
      <div class="w">
        <div style="max-width: 900px;">
          <h2 style="font-size: 42px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 32px;">The Outcome</h2>
          <div style="background: rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.15); border-radius: 4px; padding: 40px;">
            <ul style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85); list-style: none; padding: 0;">
              <li style="margin-bottom: 16px;">✓ 25-30% improvement in form-to-phone conversion</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 16px;">✓ 15-20% improvement in phone-to-consultation conversion</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 16px;">✓ Intake team that's less overwhelmed and more organized</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 16px;">✓ Better data about prospect quality that feeds back to marketing</li>
              <li>✓ On a 100-lead-per-month firm, that's 10-15 additional retained clients per month from the same marketing budget</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="padding: 60px 0; background: rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.05); border-top: 1px solid rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.15);">
      <div class="w">
        <div style="text-align: center;">
          <h3 style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 20px;">Let's Optimize Your Intake</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 15px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); margin-bottom: 28px;">
            Schedule a free consultation to review your current intake process.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 9px; background: var(--gold); color: var(--ink); font-family: var(--man); font-weight: 800; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.07em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 16px 34px; border: none; border-radius: 2px; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.25s; box-shadow: 0 4px 28px rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.42);">
            Schedule a Call →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    a:hover {
      background: var(--glt) !important;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 36px rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.52) !important;
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
